      "y": 591.0,
      "width": 327,
      "height": 75,
      "text": "Issues:\n- 4 databases to maintain (ops burden)\n- Data duplicated across stores\n- Charts Data Collector is an extra moving part\n- Elasticsearch is expensive and the wrong tool",
