    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "d7_benefits_t",
      "x": 425.5,
      "y": 741.0,
      "width": 649,
      "height": 105,
      "text": "Benefits:\n- 3 databases collapsed to 1 (TimescaleDB)\n- Charts Data Collector ELIMINATED (continuous aggregates auto-maintain rollups)\n- Same PostgreSQL tooling as Instrument Master (operational simplicity)\n- Used in production by Robinhood, Coinbase, Messari\n- Native 10x compression saves ~80% storage cost vs MongoDB",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100
